ğŸ§© How to Run

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Smart-Secure-Banking-System.git


Navigate to the project folder:

cd Smart-Secure-Banking-System


Compile the code:

gcc banking_system.c -o banking


Run the program:

./banking

